title: Classic Popeye Issue 24 (PDF) - July 2014
description:
Classic Popeye Issue 24 (PDF) - July 2014

36 Pages | PDF | English | 24 MB 


Bud Sagendorf: The world's greatest Popeye cartoonist! He does it again--his rolicking genius starts out with the feature comics story Golden Street starring Popeye and his Pappy! Plus more comics, stories and Bud Sagendorf's own creation Sherm in the thrill-packed, laugh-filled comic "The Race!" RACE to put this in your order and head to your fave local comic shop to nab it, ya swab!
